---
import Base from "../../layouts/Base.astro";
---

<Base title="MRRScope" description="SaaS metrics dashboard for indie founders. Connect Stripe and instantly see your MRR, ARR, Churn Rate, LTV and more. Free demo included.">

  <!-- Hero -->
  <section class="hero">
    <div class="container">
      <span class="badge">Built for indie founders</span>
      <h1 class="hero-title">Know your <span class="accent">MRR</span>.<br />Without the $100/mo dashboard.</h1>
      <p class="hero-subtitle">
        MRRScope connects to Stripe and shows you the SaaS metrics that actually matter.
        MRR, ARR, Churn, LTV, ARPU — all in one clean dashboard.
      </p>
      <div class="hero-actions">
        <a href="#pricing" class="btn-primary">Try Demo Free</a>
        <a href="#how-it-works" class="btn-secondary">See how it works</a>
      </div>
      <p class="hero-note">No credit card. No sign-up for demo mode.</p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Pain Points -->
  <section class="pain-section">
    <div class="container">
      <h2 class="section-title">Sound familiar?</h2>
      <div class="pain-grid">
        <div class="pain-card">
          <span class="pain-icon">&#x1f4ca;</span>
          <h3>"Stripe's dashboard doesn't show me MRR"</h3>
          <p>Stripe tracks payments, not SaaS metrics. You end up exporting CSVs and building spreadsheets just to know your monthly recurring revenue.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="pain-card">
          <span class="pain-icon">&#x1f4b8;</span>
          <h3>"Baremetrics costs more than some of my customers pay me"</h3>
          <p>$108/year minimum for the big players. When you're at $500 MRR, spending 20% of revenue on analytics feels wrong.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="pain-card">
          <span class="pain-icon">&#x1f937;</span>
          <h3>"I honestly don't know my churn rate"</h3>
          <p>You have a gut feeling, but you've never actually calculated it. You know you should, but who has the time to build a pipeline for that?</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Metrics Showcase -->
  <section class="metrics-section">
    <div class="container">
      <h2 class="section-title">Six metrics. Zero guesswork.</h2>
      <p class="section-desc">Everything you need to understand your SaaS health at a glance.</p>
      <div class="metrics-grid">
        <div class="metric-card">
          <span class="metric-value">MRR</span>
          <span class="metric-label">Monthly Recurring Revenue</span>
          <p>Your bread and butter number. See exactly how much predictable revenue you're generating each month.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="metric-card">
          <span class="metric-value">ARR</span>
          <span class="metric-label">Annual Recurring Revenue</span>
          <p>The big picture view. Great for setting yearly goals and understanding your growth trajectory.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="metric-card">
          <span class="metric-value">Churn</span>
          <span class="metric-label">Churn Rate</span>
          <p>How many customers are leaving? If you don't know this number, you're flying blind.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="metric-card">
          <span class="metric-value">LTV</span>
          <span class="metric-label">Lifetime Value</span>
          <p>How much a customer is worth over their entire relationship with you. Essential for deciding how much to spend on acquisition.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="metric-card">
          <span class="metric-value">ARPU</span>
          <span class="metric-label">Avg Revenue Per User</span>
          <p>Are your customers paying enough? ARPU helps you understand your pricing health.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="metric-card">
          <span class="metric-value">Revenue</span>
          <span class="metric-label">Breakdown & Trends</span>
          <p>Visual charts showing new, expansion, contraction, and churned revenue over time.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- How It Works -->
  <section id="how-it-works" class="how-section">
    <div class="container">
      <h2 class="section-title">Up and running in 2 minutes</h2>
      <div class="steps">
        <div class="step">
          <span class="step-num">1</span>
          <h3>Try the demo</h3>
          <p>No sign-up needed. The demo mode uses realistic sample data so you can explore every feature before connecting anything.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="step">
          <span class="step-num">2</span>
          <h3>Connect Stripe</h3>
          <p>One OAuth click. MRRScope reads your subscription data (read-only) and crunches the numbers automatically.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="step">
          <span class="step-num">3</span>
          <h3>See your metrics</h3>
          <p>MRR, ARR, Churn, LTV, ARPU and revenue breakdowns — all visualized with clean charts you can actually understand.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Pricing -->
  <section id="pricing" class="pricing-section">
    <div class="container">
      <h2 class="section-title">Simple pricing. No surprises.</h2>
      <p class="section-desc">Start free. Upgrade when you're ready to connect real data.</p>
      <div class="pricing-grid">
        <div class="price-card">
          <h3>Free</h3>
          <div class="price">$0</div>
          <p class="price-desc">forever</p>
          <ul class="price-features">
            <li>Full demo mode with sample data</li>
            <li>All 6 SaaS metrics</li>
            <li>Interactive charts</li>
            <li>No sign-up required</li>
          </ul>
          <a href="https://github.com/mvtrdmqv88-droid/mrrscope" class="btn-secondary btn-block">Try Demo</a>
        </div>
        <div class="price-card featured">
          <span class="price-badge">Most Popular</span>
          <h3>Pro</h3>
          <div class="price">$29</div>
          <p class="price-desc">one-time payment</p>
          <ul class="price-features">
            <li>Everything in Free</li>
            <li>Connect real Stripe data</li>
            <li>Automatic daily refresh</li>
            <li>Historical trend tracking</li>
            <li>Export to CSV</li>
          </ul>
          <a href="https://github.com/mvtrdmqv88-droid/mrrscope" class="btn-primary btn-block">Get Pro</a>
          <p class="price-alt">or $9.99/mo if you prefer</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- FAQ -->
  <section class="faq-section">
    <div class="container">
      <h2 class="section-title">FAQ</h2>
      <div class="faq-list">
        <details class="faq-item">
          <summary>Is my Stripe data safe?</summary>
          <p>Yes. MRRScope uses Stripe's official OAuth and only requests read-only access to subscription data. We never see your customers' payment details and we don't store raw Stripe data on our servers.</p>
        </details>
        <details class="faq-item">
          <summary>What's the difference between the demo and real data?</summary>
          <p>The demo uses realistic sample data so you can explore the full dashboard. Pro mode connects to your actual Stripe account and calculates metrics from your real subscriptions.</p>
        </details>
        <details class="faq-item">
          <summary>Why should I pick MRRScope over Baremetrics or ProfitWell?</summary>
          <p>Those are great tools if you're a funded startup. But if you're an indie founder doing $500-5,000 MRR, spending $100+/month on analytics doesn't make sense. MRRScope gives you the metrics you need at a price that works for early-stage SaaS.</p>
        </details>
        <details class="faq-item">
          <summary>Can I get a refund?</summary>
          <p>Yes. If MRRScope doesn't work for you within 14 days of purchase, email me and I'll refund you. No questions asked.</p>
        </details>
        <details class="faq-item">
          <summary>Do you support Paddle, Lemon Squeezy, or other payment processors?</summary>
          <p>Not yet — Stripe only for now. Paddle support is on the roadmap. If you want to bump the priority, open an issue on GitHub.</p>
        </details>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Bottom CTA -->
  <section class="bottom-cta">
    <div class="container">
      <h2>Stop guessing. Start knowing.</h2>
      <p>Try the demo for free. Connect Stripe when you're ready.</p>
      <a href="https://github.com/mvtrdmqv88-droid/mrrscope" class="btn-primary">Try MRRScope Free</a>
    </div>
  </section>

</Base>

<style>
  /* Hero */
  .hero {
    padding: 5rem 0 4rem;
    text-align: center;
  }
  .badge {
    display: inline-block;
    background: var(--color-border);
    color: var(--color-text-muted);
    font-size: 0.8rem;
    padding: 0.3rem 0.8rem;
    border-radius: 999px;
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
  }
  .hero-title {
    font-size: 2.75rem;
    font-weight: 800;
    line-height: 1.2;
    margin-bottom: 1.25rem;
  }
  .accent { color: var(--color-accent); }
  .hero-subtitle {
    color: var(--color-text-muted);
    font-size: 1.15rem;
    max-width: 560px;
    margin: 0 auto 2rem;
  }
  .hero-actions {
    display: flex;
    gap: 1rem;
    justify-content: center;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
    margin-bottom: 0.75rem;
  }
  .hero-note {
    color: var(--color-text-muted);
    font-size: 0.8rem;
  }

  /* Buttons */
  .btn-primary {
    display: inline-block;
    background: var(--color-accent);
    color: #fff;
    padding: 0.75rem 1.5rem;
    border-radius: 8px;
    font-weight: 600;
    transition: background 0.2s;
    text-decoration: none;
  }
  .btn-primary:hover { background: var(--color-accent-hover); text-decoration: none; }
  .btn-secondary {
    display: inline-block;
    background: transparent;
    color: var(--color-text);
    padding: 0.75rem 1.5rem;
    border-radius: 8px;
    font-weight: 600;
    border: 1px solid var(--color-border);
    transition: border-color 0.2s;
    text-decoration: none;
  }
  .btn-secondary:hover { border-color: var(--color-text-muted); text-decoration: none; }
  .btn-block { display: block; text-align: center; width: 100%; }

  /* Sections */
  .section-title {
    font-size: 1.75rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
  }
  .section-desc {
    color: var(--color-text-muted);
    margin-bottom: 2.5rem;
  }

  /* Pain Points */
  .pain-section { padding: 4rem 0; }
  .pain-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(280px, 1fr));
    gap: 1.25rem;
    margin-top: 2rem;
  }
  .pain-card {
    background: var(--color-surface);
    border: 1px solid var(--color-border);
    border-radius: 12px;
    padding: 1.5rem;
  }
  .pain-icon { font-size: 1.5rem; display: block; margin-bottom: 0.75rem; }
  .pain-card h3 {
    font-size: 1rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
    font-style: italic;
  }
  .pain-card p { color: var(--color-text-muted); font-size: 0.9rem; }

  /* Metrics */
  .metrics-section { padding: 4rem 0; }
  .metrics-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(300px, 1fr));
    gap: 1.25rem;
  }
  .metric-card {
    background: var(--color-surface);
    border: 1px solid var(--color-border);
    border-radius: 12px;
    padding: 1.5rem;
  }
  .metric-value {
    display: block;
    font-size: 1.5rem;
    font-weight: 800;
    color: var(--color-accent);
    font-family: var(--font-mono);
  }
  .metric-label {
    display: block;
    font-size: 0.8rem;
    color: var(--color-text-muted);
    margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
  }
  .metric-card p { color: var(--color-text-muted); font-size: 0.9rem; }

  /* How It Works */
  .how-section { padding: 4rem 0; }
  .steps {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(250px, 1fr));
    gap: 2rem;
    margin-top: 2rem;
  }
  .step { text-align: center; }
  .step-num {
    display: inline-flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    width: 48px;
    height: 48px;
    border-radius: 50%;
    background: var(--color-accent);
    color: #fff;
    font-weight: 800;
    font-size: 1.25rem;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
  }
  .step h3 { font-size: 1.1rem; margin-bottom: 0.5rem; }
  .step p { color: var(--color-text-muted); font-size: 0.9rem; }

  /* Pricing */
  .pricing-section {
    padding: 4rem 0;
    text-align: center;
  }
  .pricing-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(280px, 1fr));
    gap: 1.5rem;
    max-width: 700px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    text-align: left;
  }
  .price-card {
    background: var(--color-surface);
    border: 1px solid var(--color-border);
    border-radius: 12px;
    padding: 2rem;
    position: relative;
  }
  .price-card.featured { border-color: var(--color-accent); }
  .price-badge {
    position: absolute;
    top: -10px;
    right: 1rem;
    background: var(--color-accent);
    color: #fff;
    font-size: 0.7rem;
    padding: 0.2rem 0.6rem;
    border-radius: 999px;
    font-weight: 600;
  }
  .price-card h3 { font-size: 1.25rem; margin-bottom: 0.5rem; }
  .price {
    font-size: 2.5rem;
    font-weight: 800;
  }
  .price-desc {
    color: var(--color-text-muted);
    font-size: 0.85rem;
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
  }
  .price-features {
    list-style: none;
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
  }
  .price-features li {
    color: var(--color-text-muted);
    font-size: 0.9rem;
    padding: 0.3rem 0;
    padding-left: 1.25rem;
    position: relative;
  }
  .price-features li::before {
    content: "\2713";
    position: absolute;
    left: 0;
    color: var(--color-success);
    font-weight: 700;
  }
  .price-alt {
    color: var(--color-text-muted);
    font-size: 0.8rem;
    text-align: center;
    margin-top: 0.75rem;
  }

  /* FAQ */
  .faq-section { padding: 4rem 0; }
  .faq-list {
    max-width: 700px;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 1.5rem;
    margin-top: 1.5rem;
  }
  .faq-item {
    border: 1px solid var(--color-border);
    border-radius: 8px;
    overflow: hidden;
  }
  .faq-item summary {
    padding: 1rem 1.25rem;
    cursor: pointer;
    font-weight: 600;
    font-size: 0.95rem;
    background: var(--color-surface);
  }
  .faq-item summary:hover { color: var(--color-accent); }
  .faq-item p {
    padding: 0 1.25rem 1rem;
    color: var(--color-text-muted);
    font-size: 0.9rem;
  }

  /* Bottom CTA */
  .bottom-cta {
    padding: 4rem 0;
    text-align: center;
  }
  .bottom-cta h2 { font-size: 2rem; font-weight: 800; margin-bottom: 0.5rem; }
  .bottom-cta p { color: var(--color-text-muted); margin-bottom: 1.5rem; }

  /* Responsive */
  @media (max-width: 640px) {
    .hero-title { font-size: 1.75rem; }
    .hero-subtitle { font-size: 1rem; }
    .section-title { font-size: 1.35rem; }
    .price { font-size: 2rem; }
  }
</style>
